  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Buffet Breakfast</strong> features homemade pastries and cakes, jams, honey, fresh fruit, various types of bread, cold cuts, eggs, bacon, tea, coffee and fruit juices. Fruits and vegetables come from the properties own production, as do many of the other products served for breakfast.</p>
<p><strong>Dinner</strong> is four courses and uses products from the estate such as extra virgin olive oil and home grown vegetables. Dinner is a set menu but offers plenty of variety.</p>
<p>Half board is available for a supplement.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
