  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong><u>Restaurants &amp; Bars </u></strong></p>
<p><strong>Sala Rustica Restaurant </strong>has traditional Sicilian character. The chef serves delicious gastronomic creations made using organic products grown on the estate. Taste tradition Sicilian cuisine that has been re invented to create new and exciting combinations and flavours. For dinner guests can enjoy a varied set menu for lunch guests can choose from the restaurants à la carte menu and can be served beside the pool.</p>
<p>The restaurant caters for vegetarians, vegans and people with food intolerances. Please inform when booking.</p>
<p><strong>Bar </strong>serving drinks and light refreshments</p>
<p><strong><u>Pools &amp; Beaches</u></strong></p>
<p><strong>Swimming Pool </strong>The outdoor pool has a sun terrace, with views over the countryside. Relax beneath the shade of the age-old palm trees.</p>
<p><strong>Hot Tub </strong>relax and unwind in the hot tub, located in a private area with long chairs to relax on that look out into the natural surroundings. </p>
<p><strong>Beach </strong>Those looking to spend some time at the beach can head towards Gela (approx. 40-minute drive), and its 24km of golden coastline.</p>
<p><strong><u>Activities</u></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Mountain bikes, quad bikes and horse-riding excursions (local charge)</li>
<li>Small children’s playground</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><u>General Facilities</u></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Shop selling jams, local liqueurs and olive oil produced on the estate such as extra virgin olive oil and honey</li>
<li>Wifi </li>
<li>Free Parking</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
