  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms </strong>have original features such as exposed wooden beams. They are decorated in an unassuming manner and create a warm comfortable environment to relax in after days spent enjoying the surrounding area. These rooms have a shared terrace. All rooms have private shower, air conditioning, television, minibar and hairdryer. These rooms sleep up to two people.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are located on the first floor of the main building and have no balcony. Some of these rooms can sleep up to three people.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are located in a second separate building and can be on the ground floor with terrace or first floor with balcony. The rooms offer unique panoramic views over the Sicilian hills. These rooms sleep up to three people.</p>
<p>Standard rooms for single occupancy are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
